name: BigBuy
overview: BigBuy is a leading european wholesaler and dropshipper. The company, located in Spain but shipping to all Europe, was born after the union of a group of experienced companies, creating this way a leading company in the wholesale sector of original gifts, gadgets, seen-on-tv products, etc. Our mission is to distribute these products from the factories directly to our customers reducing to the minimum the marketing costs. BigBuy responds to the market demand and offers a wide range of innovative products with the highest quality at extremely competitive costs. Currently, we are known as one of the most prestigious wholesalers for a large number of manufacturers and multinational companies, that have already trusted BigBuy. BigBuy stands out as a young and enthusiastic company, thanks to a highly qualified professional staff and the best logistics facilities, which contribute to make BigBuy the main supplier for thousands of customers worldwide.
